==English==
===Pronunciation===
*snŏb, /snɒb/, /<tt>snQb</tt>/
*:[[Rhymes:English:-ɒb|Rhymes: -ɒb]]

===Noun===
'''snob''' (plural: [[snobs]])

#(disapproving) A person who seeks to be a member of the [[upper class]]es and [[look down on|looks down on]] those perceived to be of lower class.
#: ''You really are a little snob, aren't you?''
Popularized By William Makepeace Thackery-Book of Snobs-1946

